OL,3,C'Discussions taking place' over US
OL,4,Croyal visit after press dinner shooting
OL,6,FBuckingham Palace has said "a number
OL,7,Fof discussions will be taking place"
OL,8,Fwith the US after the shooting at the
OL,9,FWhite House Correspondents' dinner
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,12,FThe King and Queen are due to travel
OL,13,Fto the United States on Monday on an
OL,14,Fofficial state visit, with five in-
OL,15,Fperson meetings over four days as they
OL,16,Ftry to patch up the strained relations
OL,17,Fbetween the US and UK amid the
OL,18,Fconflict in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
