OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777227067
OL,3,C'Discussions taking place' over US
OL,4,Croyal visit after press dinner shooting
OL,6,FThe royals have contacted the US
OL,7,Fpresident "privately" and they have
OL,8,F"expressed their sympathies to those
OL,9,Faffected and gratitude to the security
OL,10,Fservices", according to the Palace.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,F"His Majesty is being kept fully
OL,18,Finformed of developments and is
OL,19,Fgreatly relieved to hear that the
OL,20,FPresident, First Lady and all guests
OL,21,Fhave been unharmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777227067
OL,3,C'Discussions taking place' over US
OL,4,Croyal visit after press dinner shooting
OL,6,F"As you would expect, a number of
OL,7,Fdiscussions will be taking place
OL,8,Fthroughout the day to discuss with US
OL,9,Fcolleagues and our respective teams to
OL,10,Fwhat degree the events of Saturday
OL,11,Fevening may or may not impact on the
OL,12,Foperational planning for the Visit,"
OL,13,Fthe statement concluded.
OL,15,FDonald Trump and other top White House
OL,16,Fofficials were evacuated from an
OL,17,Fannual dinner of the White House
OL,18,FCorrespondents' Association after a
OL,19,Fman armed with guns and knives stormed
OL,20,Fthe lobby and opened fire on Saturday
OL,21,Fnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
