OL,3,C'Discussions taking place' over US
OL,4,Croyal visit after press dinner shooting
OL,6,FThe shooting suspect was taken into
OL,7,Fcustody and identified as Cole Tomas
OL,8,FAllen, 31, from Torrance, California,
OL,9,Flaw enforcement officials said.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
